WEBVTT

1
00:09:39.830 --> 00:09:40.630 
需要多久
Time frame?

2
00:09:40.820 --> 00:09:41.990 
八到十天
Eight to ten days.

3
00:09:42.190 --> 00:09:42.950 
太久了
Too long.

4
00:09:43.510 --> 00:09:46.330 
我雇你们是让你们按照要求完成任务的
I pay you to accomplish tasks in the window required.

5
00:09:49.880 --> 00:09:53.510 
这整件事情是一起涉嫌甚广的阴谋
This entire thing is a wide ranging conspiracy.

6
00:09:53.520 --> 00:09:54.860 
阴谋
"Conspiracy"?

7
00:09:55.190 --> 00:09:56.790 
这是个四音节的词
That's a four syllable word

8
00:09:56.790 --> 00:09:58.650 
意味着你最好能证明它
which means you'd better be able to prove it.

9
00:09:58.650 --> 00:10:01.430 
并无不敬  法官大人  这儿唯一的阴谋
Respectfully, Your Honor. The only conspiracy here

10
00:10:01.430 --> 00:10:04.790 
就是控方正酝酿的那起无稽之谈
is the daft one my opposing counsel is engaging in.

11
00:10:05.010 --> 00:10:06.480 
虽然说句公道话
Though, in fairness to him,

12
00:10:06.820 --> 00:10:09.350 
那可能更多的是一种复杂的幻觉
it might be more of a complex delusion.

